completely identical function with the same (old) name

Fix docs for DescendantsOfStep1OfAbelianLieAlgebra and add an example
Stop using undocumented DualBasis from autpgrp

Make all functions read-only via BindGlobal

This avoids accidental overrides caused by other packages

commit.message:
CI: Ensure code coverage reporting will work in February 2022 and beyond

See https://github.com/gap-actions/process-coverage/issues/10
Switch CI to use GitHub Actions

Add a bunch of trivial implications

This makes various "hidden" implications created by DeclareProperty
explicit, thus fixing a bunch of warnings that show up if one starts
the upcoming GAP 4.11 with the `-N` command line option, and then
loads this package.

For some information on the background of this, see also
<https://github.com/gap-system/gap/issues/1649> and
<https://github.com/gap-system/gap/issues/2336>

Update Travis integration

Update Travis integration to use scripts from a central repository. This
allows us to apply fixes and improvements to these scripts for all
packages, and also removes some clutter from package repositories.
